<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>فِي جَنَّاتِ النَّعِيمِ <span class="c2">(١٢)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">«فِي جَنَّاتِ»</span> خبر ثان لأولئك <span class="c2">«النَّعِيمِ»</span> مضاف إليه.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
