<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>ثُلَّةٌ مِنَ الْأَوَّلِينَ <span class="c2">(١٣)</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">«ثُلَّةٌ»</span> خبر لمبتدأ محذوف <span class="c2">«مِنَ الْأَوَّلِينَ»</span> صفة ثلة.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
